{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "关羽暂时住在曹操那里，心里一直记挂刘备。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "一天，他听到刘备可能在远方，立刻决定去寻找兄长。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "曹操待他有礼，关羽也愿意把话说清楚，不让别人误会。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "离开前，关羽把收到的礼物整理好，封好书信，郑重交还。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "他说，感谢照顾，但自己早有约定，必须去找刘备。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "守信用的人，不能因为路远就忘记心里的方向。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "关羽带着刘备的家人上路。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "他没有只顾自己快走，而是放慢脚步，护送大家安全前行。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "路上遇到关口和询问，他尽量说明来意，希望少一些争执，多一些理解。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "有人劝他留下，关羽摇摇头。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "他知道朋友之间最重要的是信义，也知道家人需要平安。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "一路上，他照看车马，提醒大家休息，又把书信收在身边，不让消息丢失。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "后来，关羽终于离刘备越来越近。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "千里路并不容易，可他一步一步走下去。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "这个故事把“忠义”两个字讲得很清楚：记得承诺，照顾同行的人，也勇敢走向该去的地方。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    }
  ]
}
